  "notes": "Captures Admin GraphQL 2026-04 variant-level priceListFixedPricesAdd, priceListFixedPricesUpdate, and priceListFixedPricesDelete behavior against an existing disposable conformance price list and variant. The capture cleans any pre-existing fixed row, adds a variant fixed price, verifies downstream PriceList.prices(originType: FIXED), updates that same fixed row, verifies the updated downstream read, deletes the fixed row, and verifies the fixed-price connection is empty again. The local proxy stages each supported mutation without runtime Shopify writes and uses a cassette-backed preflight hydrate only to load the baseline price-list/product/variant records."
